It is owned by [[Greystar Real Estate Partners]] and was constructed on a build-to-rent basis.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.greystar.com/properties/charlotte-nc/ascent-uptown-apartments|title=Ascent Uptown Apartments in Charlotte|author=|date=|website=www.greystar.com|accessdate=19 October 2018}}</ref><ref>https://www.bizjournals.com/charlotte/news/2017/06/28/a-look-inside-uptown-charlottes-newest-luxury.html</ref>
